official-title.#text:
Expressing the sense of the House of Representatives that Members who vote in favor of the
			 establishment of a public, Federal Government run health insurance option
			 are urged to forgo their right to participate in the Federal Employees
			 Health Benefits Program (FEHBP) and agree to enroll under that public
			 option.
